ard Griffiths<br>Irwin ...... Geoffrey Streatfeild<br>Mrs Lintott ...... Frances de la Tour<br>The Headmaster ...... Clive Merrison<br>Crowther ...... Samuel Anderson<br>Posner ...... Samuel Barnett<br>Dakin ...... Dominic Cooper<br>Timms ...... James Corden<br>Akthar ...... Sacha Dhawan<br>Lockwood ...... Andrew Knott<br>Scripps ...... Jamie Parker<br>Rudge ...... Russell Tovey<br>Solo singer ...... Samuel Barnett<br>Pianists ...... Jamie Parker and Tom Attwood</span></div></div></div></section></section><section class="ReviewCard__tags"><ul class="CollapsableList"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/1108123?shelf=published-2004" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem">published-2004</span></a></ul></section><footer class="SocialFooter"><div data-testid="stats" class="SocialFooter__statsContainer"><div class="Button__container"><button type="button" class="Button Button--inline Button--small Button--subdued"><span class="Button__labelItem">11 likes</span></button></div><div class="Button__container"><button type="button" class="Button Button--inline Button--small Button--subdued"><span class="Button__labelItem">2 comments</span></button></div></div><div data-testid="actions"><div class="SocialFooter__action"><div class="Button__container"><button type="button" class="Button Button--inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem"><i class="Icon LikeIcon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14.4813282,6.41129383 L14.586127,6.97676447 C14.5964421,7.03541935 14.6071117,7.09675198 14.6181364,7.1607667 L14.8551301,8.60363442 L17.440983,8.60363442 C18.1623576,8.60363442 18.8218187,9.01120377 19.1444272,9.65642083 L19.1708204,9.70920723 C19.4523479,10.2722622 19.4523479,10.9350066 19.1708204,11.4980616 L19.118034,11.6036344 L19.1708204,11.7092072 C19.4523479,12.2722622 19.4523479,12.9350066 19.1708204,13.4980616 L19.118034,13.6036344 L19.1708204,13.7092072 C19.4523479,14.2722622 19.4523479,14.9350066 19.1708204,15.498